{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509970/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738923924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509970/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738923924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Medieval Archer Simulator is a most true-to-life test of skill, wherein ye taketh up bow and arrow as an archer. Train across the king\u2019s lands, hone thy aim, and prove thy worth to stand as guardian of the realm. Dost thou have the skill to prevail?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509970/extras/5e8825ff421ad2f9f041e69baac0bec0.gif?t=1738923924\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Medieval Archer Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Medieval Archer Simulator, taketh up thy bow and step into a time where skill and precision art the marks of a true archer. Roam the vast kingdom, from towering castle walls to dense, whispering forests, each offering trials to test thy mettle. With each arrow loosed, train thy hand and sharpen thine eye, that ye may prove thy worth before king and country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509970/extras/19027c497b4407f1128a6c694fa70816.gif?t=1738923924\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But mastery is not granted lightly! The path of the archer demandeth patience, for only those who train with diligence shall earn their place among the king\u2019s elite guard. With bows aplenty to wield and trials most challenging, dost thou possess the skill and fortitude to rise above all and claim glory?</p>","background":"https: